'''''Dawn, Caress the Distant Lands Once More''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[As Tomorrow Became Yesterday]].

==Steps==
# Talk to Cyrene at the beginning of the new world
# Head to the dock for one last look at the sea of Aedes Elysiae
# Listen to Cyrene's truth and complete the puzzle of "the Remembrance"

